<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <title>Request for Account Deletion</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      background-color: #fff;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }

    .email-header {
      background-color: #E74C3C;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .email-footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #777;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #E74C3C;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .direct-link {
      margin-top: 10px;
      color: #777;
      font-size: 14px;
      word-wrap: break-word;
      overflow-wrap: break-word;
    }

    a.direct-link {
      color: #3498db;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    a.direct-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-container">
  <div class="email-header">
    <h1>Request for Account Deletion</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="email-body">
    <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
    <p>We have received your request to delete your account from our system.</p>
    <p>If this was you, please confirm the deletion of your account by using the code below:</p>
    <p><strong>Code: {{code}}</strong></p>
    <p>If you did not make this request, please ignore this email, and your account will remain active.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="email-footer">
    <p>&copy; 2024 - Quizzfly. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
